text: Styrkeprøven , also called Den Store Styrkeprøven -LRB- The Great Trial of Strength -RRB- , is a 540 km long bicycle cyclosportive which starts in Trondheim and finishes in Oslo , Norway . It was first held in 1967 , initiaded by Erik Gjems-Onstad and has taken place since then in late June every year .   In 2012 the record time was 12.51,02 .
